  "decision": "Reject this mixed wrapper as a promotion. TurboEPBackend remains useful as a raw no-helper DeepSeek EP edge, but bolting it under the existing hot-helper wrapper is slower than raw Turbo no-helper and much slower than standard-EP hot-helper.",
